All Implemented Interfaces:
javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.IterationTag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.JspTag, javax.servlet.jsp.tagext.Tag
public abstract class TrinidadValidatorELTag
extends TrinidadTagSupport

This is the Trinidad version of the JSF ValidatorELTag class. The main difference is that this class is NOT inheriting from the standard TagSupport and therefore does not implement Serializable interface.

Apache MyFaces team
